 
* {} /* reset everything to prevent default browser behavior */
body {} /* use in body to let children inherit */
transform: translate(-50%, -50%); /* shift -50% of element prop */
ease-in: faster; ease-out: slower over time
backface-visibility: hidden; prevent animation shaking
transform: from top left
box-shadow: x y blur color
animation-fill-mode: backwards; apply style before animation start; (we use animation-delay before)
inline-ids-classes/pseudo clases-element 0-0-0-0 .btn:hover = 2. Last code will be applied if same specificity

- rem is relative to root font-size.
- em are measured relative to their parent font-size, if used to specify font-size
- em are measured relative to the current font-size, if used to specify lengths
- inherit: font-size, font-family
- always define img with perventage to scale nicely with the view port
